Title: Pending
Description: The DPS has been proposed, but is not yet in force. It might be awaiting signature.

Title: Active
Description: The DPS has started for all participants.

Title: Cancelled
Description: This DPS has been cancelled prior to starting.

Title: Terminated
Description: This DPS had started, and has now come to a close. This might be due to its successful completion, or might be early termination due to some non-completion.
